Body: Date: Tue, 10 Dec 1996 21:21:42 GMT Server: NCSA/1.4.2 Content-type: text/html Last-modified: Mon, 04 Sep 1995 19:47:16 GMT Content-length: 3084 Upper and Lower Bounds on Constructing Alphabetic Binary Trees Next: Overview Upper and Lower Bounds on Constructing Alphabetic Binary Trees MARIA KLAWE and BRENDAN MUMEY Abstract: This paper studies the long-standing open question of whether optimal alphabetic binary trees can be constructed in time.
